author: Nerdstalgic
description:
For 12 seasons, The Big Bang Theory dominated television, becoming one of the most successful sitcoms in history. With two spin-offs, countless iconic episodes, and a cultural impact that still lingers, it’s no wonder this show cemented itself as a true TV juggernaut.

In this compilation, we take a deep dive into the extreme highs and devastating lows of The Big Bang Theory. From its funniest episodes and best character arcs to the behind-the-scenes reasons why the show finally came to an end, this is the ultimate look back at one of the biggest sitcoms of the last 15 years.

Who’s YOUR favorite Big Bang Theory character? Sheldon? Penny? Howard? Drop your thoughts in the comments below!
